        "text": "Prince Edward Island Tax Centre ",
        "w": 158.89,
        "x": 21.17,
        "y": 664.33,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "or the ",
        "w": 28.85,
        "x": 179.56,
        "y": 664.33,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Sudbury Tax Centre",
        "w": 95.52,
        "x": 207.91,
        "y": 664.33,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": ". The tax centres are listed at",
        "w": 129.45,
        "x": 302.93,
        "y": 664.33,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "canada.ca/tax-centres",
        "w": 104.99,
        "x": 434.66,
        "y": 664.33,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": ".",
        "w": 3.28,
        "x": 539.15,
        "y": 664.33,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "For more information, go to ",
        "w": 123.88,
        "x": 21.17,
        "y": 646.61,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "canada.ca/business-number",
        "w": 134.99,
        "x": 144.55,
        "y": 646.61,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "or call ",
        "w": 29.95,
        "x": 281.82,
        "y": 646.61,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "1-800-959-5525",
        "w": 71.65,
        "x": 311.27,
        "y": 646.61,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": ".",
        "w": 3.28,
        "x": 382.42,
        "y": 646.61,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Do",
        "w": 13.28,
        "x": 21.01,
        "y": 628.63,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "not",
        "w": 16.05,
        "x": 36.57,
        "y": 628.63,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": " use this form ",
        "w": 63.3,
        "x": 52.12,
        "y": 628.63,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "if both ",
        "w": 33.83,
        "x": 114.92,
        "y": 628.63,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "of the following apply to you:",
        "w": 126.68,
        "x": 148.25,
        "y": 628.63,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.97,
        "text": "You are a selected listed financial institution (SLFI) for goods and services tax/harmonized sales tax (GST/HST) ",
        "w": 508.11,
        "x": 43.26,
        "y": 616.25,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "purposes or Quebec sales tax (QST) purposes, or both",
        "w": 243.94,
        "x": 54.01,
        "y": 604.25,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.61,
        "text": "You want to register for GST/HST and QST purposes or you are already registered for GST/HST purposes and want to ",
        "w": 539.81,
        "x": 43.26,
        "y": 589.61,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "register for QST purposes only.",
        "w": 139.44,
        "x": 54.01,
        "y": 577.61,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Instead, use form RC7301, Request for a Business Number and Certain Program Accounts for Certain Selected Listed Financial ",
        "w": 570.18,
        "x": 21.01,
        "y": 560.23,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Institutions. For more information, including the definition of an SLFI for GST/HST ",
        "w": 363.43,
        "x": 21.01,
        "y": 548.23,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "and",
        "w": 18.28,
        "x": 383.94,
        "y": 548.23,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": " QST purposes, ",
        "w": 73.31,
        "x": 401.72,
        "y": 548.23,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "go to ",
        "w": 25.52,
        "x": 21.01,
        "y": 536.23,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "canada.ca/gst-hst-financial-institutions",
        "w": 186.09,
        "x": 46.03,
        "y": 536.23,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": ".",
        "w": 3.28,
        "x": 231.62,
        "y": 536.23,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Note:",
        "w": 26.05,
        "x": 21.01,
        "y": 521.12,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "If your business is in the province of Quebec and you are registering for a GST/HST program account, do not use this ",
        "w": 522.41,
        "x": 49.34,
        "y": 521.12,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "form. Instead, contact Revenu Québec, unless you are an SLFI. If you are an SLFI and you are only registering for the ",
        "w": 525.22,
        "x": 49.01,
        "y": 509.12,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "GST/HST program account that will not include QST information, use this form unless you are registering because you are ",
        "w": 544.05,
        "x": 49.01,
        "y": 497.12,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "making or joining a consolidated filing election.",
        "w": 206.7,
        "x": 49.01,
        "y": 485.12,
      },
      {
        "h": 15,
        "text": "Register for a business number",
        "w": 180.65,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 461.64,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "I want to register for a business number (BN) ",
        "w": 202.24,
        "x": 54.01,
        "y": 446.22,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Part A",
        "w": 28.29,
        "x": 54.01,
        "y": 434.22,
      },
      {
        "h": 15,
        "text": "Register for program accounts",
        "w": 175.97,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 414.26,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "I want to register for the following program accounts (tick all that apply):",
        "w": 316.18,
        "x": 21.01,
        "y": 401.38,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "GST/HST (RT) ",
        "w": 69.39,
        "x": 54,
        "y": 383.84,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Part B",
        "w": 28.29,
        "x": 54,
        "y": 370.84,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Payroll deductions (RP) ",
        "w": 108.31,
        "x": 243.01,
        "y": 383.84,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Part C",
        "w": 28.84,
        "x": 243.01,
        "y": 370.84,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Corporation (RC) ",
        "w": 79.4,
        "x": 438.01,
        "y": 383.84,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Part D",
        "w": 28.84,
        "x": 438.01,
        "y": 370.84,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Information return (RZ) ",
        "w": 104.97,
        "x": 54,
        "y": 350.84,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Part E",
        "w": 28.29,
        "x": 54,
        "y": 337.84,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Import-export (RM) ",
        "w": 87.73,
        "x": 243.01,
        "y": 350.84,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Part F",
        "w": 27.73,
        "x": 243.01,
        "y": 337.84,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Charity (RR) ",
        "w": 58.83,
        "x": 438.01,
        "y": 350.84,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Part G",
        "w": 29.4,
        "x": 438.01,
        "y": 337.84,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Note:",
        "w": 26.05,
        "x": 21.01,
        "y": 323.02,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.97,
        "text": "You must have a BN if you only want to register for program accounts.",
        "w": 321.94,
        "x": 43.26,
        "y": 311.99,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.97,
        "text": "To register for additional payroll deductions, information return, import-export, or charity program accounts, fill in another ",
        "w": 545.34,
        "x": 43.26,
        "y": 299.99,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "part C, E, F, or G, as applicable, of another form RC1 and attach it to this form.",
        "w": 348.99,
        "x": 54.01,
        "y": 287.99,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "You do not need to fill in Part D if you incorporated your business federally or with a province which has partnered with ",
        "w": 537.04,
        "x": 43.26,
        "y": 276.46,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "the Canada Revenue Agency (CRA). If this is the case, a BN and a corporation income tax program account (RC) will be ",
        "w": 536.27,
        "x": 54.01,
        "y": 264.46,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "automatically assigned to you by the CRA. For a list of the provinces that have partnered with the CRA, ",
        "w": 459.04,
        "x": 54.01,
        "y": 252.46,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "go to ",
        "w": 25.52,
        "x": 54.01,
        "y": 240.46,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "canada.ca/business-number",
        "w": 134.99,
        "x": 79.03,
        "y": 240.46,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": " and click on "When you need a business number or Canada Revenue Agency ",
        "w": 350.89,
        "x": 213.52,
        "y": 240.46,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "program accounts." Then click on "Corporation income tax (RC)."",
        "w": 288.46,
        "x": 54.01,
        "y": 228.46,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "By giving us your email address, you are signing up to receive email notifications from the CRA. Once signed up, we",
        "w": 525.35,
        "x": 43.26,
        "y": 216.46,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "stop sending you most CRA mail on paper. Instead, we send you an email when notices, letters, and statements are ",
        "w": 516.3,
        "x": 54.01,
        "y": 204.46,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "available in My Business Account. To register for My Business Account, go to",
        "w": 342.86,
        "x": 54.01,
        "y": 192.46,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": " canada.ca/my-cra-business-account",
        "w": 175.56,
        "x": 396.37,
        "y": 192.46,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": ".",
        "w": 3.28,
        "x": 571.43,
        "y": 192.46,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Based on your selections, please fill in the following parts:",
        "w": 256.17,
        "x": 21.01,
        "y": 176.99,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.58,
        "text": "Part A,",
        "w": 41.82,
