  {
    "blocks": [
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Protected B ",
        "w": 59.4,
        "x": 459.29,
        "y": 763.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "when completed",
        "w": 73.31,
        "x": 518.19,
        "y": 763.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 10,
        "text": "Page 4 of 13",
        "w": 45.77,
        "x": 545.63,
        "y": 15.78,
      },
      {
        "h": 15,
        "text": "Part A – General business information (continued)",
        "w": 287.33,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 737.2,
      },
      {
        "h": 13.75,
        "text": "Part A5 – GST/HST information",
        "w": 162.53,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 710.19,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Do you provide or plan to provide property or services in Canada or to export outside Canada? ",
        "w": 421.25,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 691.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "If",
        "w": 6.06,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 679.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "no",
        "w": 12.72,
        "x": 35.34,
        "y": 679.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": ", you generally cannot register for GST/HST. However, certain businesses may be able to ",
        "w": 399.55,
        "x": 47.56,
        "y": 679.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "register.",
        "w": 36.62,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 667.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Yes",
        "w": 17.73,
        "x": 519,
        "y": 687.66,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "No",
        "w": 13.28,
        "x": 567,
        "y": 687.66,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Are your total annual revenues from your worldwide taxable supplies, including those of any ",
        "w": 408.46,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 631.41,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "associates, more than $30,000? If ",
        "w": 153.92,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 619.41,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "yes",
        "w": 17.18,
        "x": 180.42,
        "y": 619.41,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": ", you ",
        "w": 24.96,
        "x": 197.1,
        "y": 619.41,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "must",
        "w": 24.39,
        "x": 221.56,
        "y": 619.41,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": " register for GST/HST, unless you are a non-",
        "w": 198.91,
        "x": 245.45,
        "y": 619.41,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "resident and do not carry on business in Canada for GST/HST purposes. ",
        "w": 325.65,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 607.41,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Note:",
        "w": 26.05,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 583.41,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": " Special rules apply to public service bodies.",
        "w": 196.69,
        "x": 52.55,
        "y": 583.41,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Yes",
        "w": 17.73,
        "x": 519,
        "y": 627.66,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "No",
        "w": 13.28,
        "x": 567,
        "y": 627.66,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Are you a public service body whose total annual revenues from worldwide taxable supplies, ",
        "w": 411.23,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 550.41,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "including those of any associates, are more than $50,000? If ",
        "w": 270.65,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 538.41,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "yes",
        "w": 17.18,
        "x": 297.15,
        "y": 538.41,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": ", you ",
        "w": 24.96,
        "x": 313.83,
        "y": 538.41,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "must",
        "w": 24.39,
        "x": 338.29,
        "y": 538.41,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": " register for GST/HST. ",
        "w": 102.75,
        "x": 362.18,
        "y": 538.41,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Note:",
        "w": 26.05,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 514.41,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": " Special rules apply to charities and public institutions with respect to the qualification of ",
        "w": 390.12,
        "x": 52.55,
        "y": 514.41,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "these organizations as a small supplier.",
        "w": 175.57,
        "x": 56,
        "y": 502.41,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Yes",
        "w": 17.73,
        "x": 519,
        "y": 546.66,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "No",
        "w": 13.28,
        "x": 567,
        "y": 546.66,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Are all the property and services you sell or provide exempt from GST/HST? ",
        "w": 340.62,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 469.35,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Note",
        "w": 22.72,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 445.35,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": ": In general, when you sell or provide only exempt property and services, you cannot register ",
        "w": 412.35,
        "x": 49.22,
        "y": 445.35,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "for the GST/HST, unless you are a listed financial institution resident in Canada.",
        "w": 353.99,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 433.35,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Yes",
        "w": 17.73,
        "x": 519,
        "y": 465.66,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "No",
        "w": 13.28,
        "x": 567,
        "y": 465.66,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Do you operate a taxi, commercial ride-sharing, or limousine service?",
        "w": 307.26,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 400.41,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "If",
        "w": 6.06,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 388.41,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "yes",
        "w": 17.18,
        "x": 35.34,
        "y": 388.41,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": ", you ",
        "w": 24.96,
        "x": 52.02,
        "y": 388.41,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "must",
        "w": 24.39,
        "x": 76.48,
        "y": 388.41,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": " register for GST/HST, regardless of your revenue. ",
        "w": 227.25,
        "x": 100.37,
        "y": 388.41,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Yes",
        "w": 17.73,
        "x": 519,
        "y": 396.66,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "No",
        "w": 13.28,
        "x": 567,
        "y": 396.66,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Are you an individual whose sole activity subject to GST/HST is from commercial rental income?",
        "w": 426.19,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 355.25,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Yes",
        "w": 17.73,
        "x": 519,
        "y": 351.66,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "No",
        "w": 13.28,
        "x": 567,
        "y": 351.66,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Are you a non-resident?",
        "w": 107.22,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 316.24,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Yes",
        "w": 17.73,
        "x": 519,
        "y": 312.65,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "No",
        "w": 13.28,
        "x": 567,
        "y": 312.65,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Are you a non-resident who enters Canada to directly supply taxable admissions to a place of ",
        "w": 416.25,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 277.4,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "amusement, a seminar, an activity, or an event held in Canada? If ",
        "w": 294.53,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 265.4,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "yes",
        "w": 17.18,
        "x": 321.03,
        "y": 265.4,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": ", you ",
        "w": 24.96,
        "x": 337.71,
        "y": 265.4,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "must",
        "w": 24.39,
        "x": 362.17,
        "y": 265.4,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": " register for",
        "w": 51.07,
        "x": 386.06,
        "y": 265.4,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "GST/HST, regardless of your revenue.",
        "w": 171.12,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 253.4,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Yes",
        "w": 17.73,
        "x": 519,
        "y": 273.65,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "No",
        "w": 13.28,
        "x": 567,
        "y": 273.65,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Do you wish to register voluntarily? By registering voluntarily, you ",
        "w": 291.71,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 218.85,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "must",
        "w": 24.39,
        "x": 318.21,
        "y": 218.85,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "begin to charge GST/HST ",
        "w": 118.33,
        "x": 344.88,
        "y": 218.85,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "on your taxable supplies, other than zero-rated supplies, made in Canada and file returns even if ",
        "w": 429.6,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 206.85,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "your total annual revenues from your worldwide taxable supplies are $30,000 or less ($50,000 or ",
        "w": 430.14,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 194.85,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "less if you are a public service body).",
        "w": 164.45,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 182.85,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Yes",
        "w": 17.73,
        "x": 519,
        "y": 216.65,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "No",
        "w": 13.28,
        "x": 567,
        "y": 216.65,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Are you an SLFI that is required to be registered for GST/HST because you are making a reporting ",
        "w": 439.59,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 148.25,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "entity election or a tax adjustment transfer election, and you are not making a consolidated filing ",
        "w": 426.82,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 136.25,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "election or electing to be added to an existing consolidated filing election?",
        "w": 326.23,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 124.25,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Yes",
        "w": 17.73,
        "x": 519,
        "y": 144.66,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "No",
        "w": 13.28,
        "x": 567,
        "y": 144.66,
      },
    ],
    "page": 4,
  },
  {
    "blocks": [
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Protected B ",
        "w": 59.4,
        "x": 459.29,
        "y": 763.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "when completed",
        "w": 73.31,
        "x": 518.19,
        "y": 763.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 10,
        "text": "Page 5 of 13",
        "w": 45.77,
        "x": 545.63,
        "y": 15.78,
      },
      {
        "h": 15,
        "text": "Part B – Registering for a GST/HST program account (RT)",
        "w": 328.66,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 737.2,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "If you want to register for a separate GST/HST program account for a branch or division of a head office, fill in form GST10, ",
        "w": 547.96,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 715.61,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Application or Revocation of the Authorization to File Separate GST/HST Returns and Rebate Applications for Branches or ",
        "w": 545.19,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 703.61,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Divisions.",
        "w": 43.28,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 691.61,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Note:",
        "w": 26.05,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 673.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": " More information must be provided if the effective date of registration indicated below is more than 30 days before the ",
        "w": 525.75,
        "x": 52.55,
        "y": 673.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "date of application for registration. Usually, depending on the business's situation, you must provide one of the following:",
        "w": 532.12,
        "x": 54,
        "y": 661.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 13.34,
        "text": "sale invoices or other documents proving that the business began charging the GST/HST on the effective date entered ",
        "w": 538.07,
        "x": 55.25,
        "y": 645.41,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "on this form if you are voluntarily registering for the GST/HST",
        "w": 271.15,
        "x": 65.88,
        "y": 634.25,
      },
      {
        "h": 13.3,
        "text": "a document (a balance sheet, a financial statement, or an information slip) proving that the business is required to ",
        "w": 516.37,
        "x": 55.25,
        "y": 615.41,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "register for GST/HST purposes because its revenues from taxable supplies, including zero-rated supplies, exceeded ",
        "w": 517.38,
        "x": 65.88,
        "y": 604.21,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "$30,000 (or $50,000 for a public service body) over the last four calendar quarters or in a single calendar quarter",
        "w": 497.4,
        "x": 65.88,
        "y": 592.21,
      },
      {
        "h": 13.75,
        "text": "Part B1 – GST/HST program account identification",
        "w": 263.38,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 564.69,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "If the information is the same as in Part A3, tick this box.",
        "w": 249.5,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 544.41,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "If you want to use a separate name for this program account, enter the name.",
        "w": 342.9,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 522.66,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Email address (for information on how we will use your email address, see page 1)",
        "w": 365.63,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 492.66,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Physical business location",
        "w": 117.21,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 462.66,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "City",
        "w": 17.72,
        "x": 411.01,
        "y": 462.66,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Province, territory, or state",
        "w": 117.76,
        "x": 27.01,
        "y": 432.66,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Country",
        "w": 35.51,
        "x": 297,
        "y": 432.66,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Postal or ZIP code",
        "w": 67.96,
        "x": 509.94,
        "y": 432.5,
      },
      {
        "h": 13,
        "text": "Mailing address (if different from the physical business location) for GST/HST purposesCity",
        "w": 401.72,
        "x": 27.01,
        "y": 402.66,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Province, territory, or state",
        "w": 117.76,
        "x": 27.01,
        "y": 372.66,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Country",
        "w": 35.51,
