        "y": 340.16,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Canadian amateur athletic association (CAAA)",
        "w": 206.69,
        "x": 54,
        "y": 322.16,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "National arts service organization (NASO)",
        "w": 186.11,
        "x": 54,
        "y": 304.16,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Note:",
        "w": 25.53,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 286.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Having an RR program account does not mean you are a registered charity, a registered CAAA or a registered NASO. ",
        "w": 525.96,
        "x": 43.25,
        "y": 271.75,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Before you can operate as a registered charity, a registered CAAA or a registered NASO, you ",
        "w": 408.46,
        "x": 54,
        "y": 259.75,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "must",
        "w": 23.9,
        "x": 461.98,
        "y": 259.75,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": " apply under the ",
        "w": 73.49,
        "x": 485.39,
        "y": 259.75,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Income Tax Act and be approved by the CRA.",
        "w": 200.4,
        "x": 54,
        "y": 247.75,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.53,
        "text": "Even if a NASO has an RR program account and is registered by the CRA under the Income Tax Act, it will not be ",
        "w": 507.45,
        "x": 43.25,
        "y": 232.69,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "considered a charity for GST/HST purposes. However, a registered CAAA is a charity for GST/HST purposes.",
        "w": 475.96,
        "x": 54,
        "y": 220.69,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "To complete the application process, you ",
        "w": 181.33,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 199.75,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "must",
        "w": 23.9,
        "x": 207.84,
        "y": 199.75,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": " add your new program account to your Business Number profile. To do this, log ",
        "w": 350.17,
        "x": 231.26,
        "y": 199.75,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "into the CRA's My Business Account service and submit your online application for registration in the "Registered Charity" ",
        "w": 529.46,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 187.75,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "section.",
        "w": 34.26,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 175.75,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
