        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "taxpayer",
        "w": 38.85,
        "x": 95,
        "y": 441.22,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "administrator, executor, liquidator, power of attorney, trustee, or legal guardian ",
        "w": 350.1,
        "x": 95,
        "y": 422.41,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "or parent of a taxpayer under the age of 16",
        "w": 190.62,
        "x": 95,
        "y": 410.41,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Choose the appropriate option (for a ",
        "w": 163.92,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 391.33,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "business",
        "w": 43.85,
        "x": 190.42,
        "y": 391.33,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "):",
        "w": 6.61,
        "x": 233.77,
        "y": 391.33,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "I am the:",
        "w": 41.62,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 372.41,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "owner",
        "w": 27.73,
        "x": 95,
        "y": 372.22,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "corporate director, corporate officer, individual with delegated authority, officer ",
        "w": 347.87,
        "x": 95,
        "y": 353.41,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "of a non-profit organization, partner of a partnership, or trustee of a trust",
        "w": 318.44,
        "x": 95,
        "y": 341.41,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "This form will not be processed",
        "w": 146.02,
        "x": 28.42,
        "y": 321.21,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": " if your name does not match the one in our records. To avoid processing delays, verify ",
        "w": 378.02,
        "x": 173.96,
        "y": 321.21,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "before",
        "w": 30.75,
        "x": 551.48,
        "y": 321.21,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": " ",
        "w": 3.25,
        "x": 581.73,
        "y": 321.21,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "signing this form that we have complete and valid information on file for you. ",
        "w": 336.14,
        "x": 28.41,
        "y": 309.21,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "First name",
        "w": 47.73,
        "x": 28,
        "y": 287.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Last name",
        "w": 47.19,
        "x": 238,
        "y": 287.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Telephone number",
        "w": 84.43,
        "x": 448,
        "y": 287.41,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "I certify that the information given on this form is correct and complete.",
        "w": 311.74,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 253.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Signature:",
        "w": 46.08,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 230.03,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Date (YYYYMMDD):",
        "w": 91.62,
        "x": 394,
        "y": 229.16,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Mailing address (if you are signing this form on behalf of an individual or trust)City",
        "w": 383.72,
        "x": 28,
        "y": 204.66,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Province, territory, or state",
        "w": 117.76,
        "x": 28,
        "y": 168.66,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Country",
        "w": 35.51,
        "x": 277,
        "y": 168.66,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Postal or ZIP code",
        "w": 81.93,
        "x": 499,
        "y": 168.66,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Once completed, ",
        "w": 77.29,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 133.63,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "send this form to your tax centre",
        "w": 152.97,
        "x": 103.8,
        "y": 133.63,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": " within ",
        "w": 30.99,
        "x": 256.28,
        "y": 133.63,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "six months",
        "w": 52.22,
        "x": 286.78,
        "y": 133.63,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": " of the date it was signed or it will not be processed.",
        "w": 224.91,
        "x": 338.51,
        "y": 133.63,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": " ",
        "w": 3.21,
        "x": 562.92,
        "y": 133.63,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "For more information, see page 4.",
        "w": 145.08,
        "x": 27,
        "y": 121.63,
      },
      {
        "h": 10,
        "text": "Personal information (including the SIN) is collected for the purposes of the administration or enforcement of the Income Tax Act, the Excise Tax Act, the Tax ",
        "w": 557.98,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 99.78,
      },
      {
        "h": 10,
        "text": "Administration Act, and related programs and activities including administering tax, benefits, audit, compliance, and collection. The information collected may be ",
        "w": 567.3,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 90.78,
      },
      {
        "h": 10,
        "text": "used or disclosed for purposes of other federal acts that provide for the imposition and collection of a tax or duty. It may also be disclosed to other federal, ",
        "w": 546,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 81.78,
      },
      {
        "h": 10,
        "text": "provincial, territorial or foreign government institutions to the extent authorized by law. Failure to provide this information may result in interest payable, penalties ",
        "w": 568.63,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 72.78,
      },
      {
        "h": 10,
        "text": "or other actions. Under the Privacy Act, individuals have the right to access their personal information, request correction, or file a complaint to the Privacy ",
        "w": 546.85,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 63.78,
      },
      {
        "h": 10,
        "text": "Commissioner of Canada regarding the handling of the individual's personal information. Refer to Personal Information Bank CRA PPU 005, CRA PPU 015, ",
        "w": 553.52,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 54.78,
      },
      {
        "h": 10,
        "text": "CRA PPU 047, CRA PPU 063, CRA PPU 094, CRA PPU 140, CRA PPU 178 and CRA PPU 218 on Info Source at",
        "w": 405.9,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 45.78,
      },
      {
        "h": 10,
        "text": " canada.ca/cra-info-source",
        "w": 101.77,
        "x": 426.5,
        "y": 45.78,
      },
      {
        "h": 10,
        "text": ".",
        "w": 2.62,
        "x": 527.87,
        "y": 45.78,
      },
      {
        "h": 10,
        "text": "Page 2 of 4",
        "w": 41.32,
        "x": 550.08,
        "y": 20.28,
      },
    ],
    "page": 2,
  },
  {
    "blocks": [
      {
        "h": 15,
        "text": "When to use this form",
        "w": 126.61,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 755.66,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.89,
        "text": "The Canada Revenue Agency (CRA) needs your permission to A program account number has three parts:",
        "w": 484.92,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 739.33,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "deal with a representative. ",
        "w": 120,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 727.33,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Use this form",
        "w": 64.4,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 709.63,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": " ",
        "w": 3.28,
        "x": 84.9,
        "y": 709.63,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "to ",
        "w": 12.72,
        "x": 87.68,
        "y": 709.63,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "give a representative access to the following ",
        "w": 199.48,
        "x": 99.9,
        "y": 709.63,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "accounts by telephone, fax, and mail:",
        "w": 165.59,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 697.63,
      },
      {
