        "w": 154.45,
        "x": 36,
        "y": 646.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Do not use ",
        "w": 54.95,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 625.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "this form",
        "w": 38.84,
        "x": 75.45,
        "y": 625.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": " ",
        "w": 3.28,
        "x": 113.79,
        "y": 625.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "to authorize a third party to act on your ",
        "w": 174.48,
        "x": 116.57,
        "y": 625.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "behalf for tax ruling or interpretation requests. For more ",
        "w": 248.38,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 613.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "information, see Income Tax Information Circular IC70-6R9, ",
        "w": 267.81,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 601.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Advance Income Tax Rulings and Technical Interpretations, or ",
        "w": 279.51,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 589.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "GST/HST Memorandum 1.4, Excise and GST/HST Rulings ",
        "w": 264.47,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 577.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "and Interpretations Service.",
        "w": 122.78,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 565.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Do not use",
        "w": 52.17,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 544.63,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": " this form ",
        "w": 44.4,
        "x": 72.67,
        "y": 544.63,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "if both",
        "w": 31.05,
        "x": 116.57,
        "y": 544.63,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": " of the following apply:",
        "w": 99.44,
        "x": 147.12,
        "y": 544.63,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "•",
        "w": 4,
        "x": 28.25,
        "y": 526.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "You are a selected listed financial institution (SLFI) for ",
        "w": 242.27,
        "x": 36,
        "y": 526.33,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "goods and services tax/harmonized sales tax (GST/HST) ",
        "w": 255.59,
        "x": 36,
        "y": 514.33,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "purposes, or Quebec sales tax (QST) purposes, or both",
        "w": 246.72,
        "x": 36,
        "y": 502.33,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "•",
        "w": 4,
        "x": 28.25,
        "y": 487.28,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "You have a GST/HST (RT) program account that ",
        "w": 220.03,
        "x": 36,
        "y": 487.33,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "includes QST information",
        "w": 112.76,
        "x": 36,
        "y": 475.33,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Instead, use form RC7259, Business Consent for Certain ",
        "w": 255.61,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 457.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Selected Listed Financial Institutions. For more information, ",
        "w": 266.16,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 445.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "including the definition of an SLFI for GST/HST ",
        "w": 211.71,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 433.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "and",
        "w": 18.28,
        "x": 232.21,
        "y": 433.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": " QST ",
        "w": 26.62,
        "x": 249.99,
        "y": 433.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "purposes, go to",
        "w": 66.65,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 421.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": " canada.ca/gst-hst-financial-institutions",
        "w": 192.09,
        "x": 87.15,
        "y": 421.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": ".",
        "w": 3.28,
        "x": 278.3,
        "y": 421.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "Only ",
        "w": 25.51,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 400.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "complete a new form if there are changes. ",
        "w": 190.03,
        "x": 46.01,
        "y": 400.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 15,
        "text": "Your responsibilities",
        "w": 119.3,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 371.67,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "You should have a list of people with ",
        "w": 165.59,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 355.68,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "proper authority",
        "w": 77.73,
        "x": 186.09,
        "y": 355.68,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": " for you ",
        "w": 36.63,
        "x": 263.32,
        "y": 355.68,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "or your business. If your list changes, you need to let us know ",
        "w": 276.19,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 343.68,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "right away. Send us official documents about the change so ",
        "w": 267.31,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 331.68,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "our records on you or your business are up to date. Other ",
        "w": 257.85,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 319.68,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "responsibilities include:",
        "w": 103.31,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 307.68,
      },
      {
        "h": 15.54,
        "text": "•making sure that the list of people with proper authority to the following:",
        "w": 342.61,
        "x": 28.25,
        "y": 286.68,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "sign this form is up to date in our files",
        "w": 165.57,
        "x": 36,
        "y": 277.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "•keeping representative information up to date",
        "w": 208.91,
        "x": 28.25,
        "y": 262.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "•monitoring and understanding what your representative is ",
        "w": 265.59,
        "x": 28.25,
        "y": 247.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "doing on your behalf for you or your business",
        "w": 197.82,
        "x": 36,
        "y": 235.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "•reviewing services to which your representative has access",
        "w": 270.56,
        "x": 28.25,
        "y": 220.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "•deciding if your representative should continue to ",
        "w": 228.36,
        "x": 28.25,
        "y": 205.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "represent you or your business",
        "w": 137.78,
        "x": 36,
        "y": 193.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "To see the type of access your representative has, go to ",
        "w": 252.3,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 175.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "canada.ca/cra-login-services.",
        "w": 140.01,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 163.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": " We may add new services that ",
        "w": 142.22,
        "x": 160.51,
        "y": 163.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "your representative can access with your consent. ",
        "w": 225.04,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 151.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 15,
        "text": "Delegated authority",
        "w": 112.62,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 119.67,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "To authorize a delegated authority, see the online services:",
        "w": 262.3,
        "x": 21,
        "y": 103.72,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "•",
        "w": 4,
        "x": 28.25,
        "y": 88.28,
      },
      {
        "h": 12.5,
        "text": "My Business Account at  ",
        "w": 109.99,
        "x": 36,
        "y": 88.72,
      },
      {
